Saturday, January 24th- KidSport Meet 
Winona Middle School-gym
1570 Homer Rd. (Winona Middle School)
Winona MN
Doors Open: 1:30pm
*gymnasts and coaches can enter through the small gym (no parents allowed please)

Sock grams, candy grams and concessions available. Meet t-shirts and sweatshirts are available for purchase prior to meet.
